## 4. Do most people prefer to travel in a modern city or a historical city?

I think both types are popular, but younger travelers may prefer modern cities because they enjoy shopping, technology, nightlife, and modern attractions. Cities like Shanghai or Tokyo are very attractive to young people.

On the other hand, historical cities are also popular because they allow people to learn about culture and history. Older travelers, in particular, may prefer places with traditional architecture and historical significance. Personally, I think many people nowadays enjoy combining both experiences in one trip.

### 中文：

我觉得这两种城市都很受欢迎，不过年轻游客可能更喜欢现代城市，因为他们喜欢购物、科技感、夜生活以及现代化景点。像上海或东京这样的城市对年轻人就特别有吸引力。

另一方面，历史城市也很受欢迎，因为它们能让人了解文化和历史。尤其是年纪较大的人，可能更喜欢有传统建筑和历史意义的地方。我个人觉得现在很多人喜欢在一次旅行中同时体验现代和历史两种风格。
